<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.1 (STRIP 1) MACHENGYUAN 9: 169 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a.1">王適（[古邑]）之行;</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a.2">楚邦少安.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a.3">君王焉先居灾（巢?）亂之上，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a.4">以觀師徒.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a.5">焉命師</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a.6">徒殺取禽獸雉兔</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-1a.7">師徒乃亂, 不【1】[...]</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.2 (STRIP 14) MACHENGYUAN 9: 182 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.1">[...] 動之於後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.2">以遌王卒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.3">三鼓乃行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.4">深入王卒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.5">不止,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.6">遂鼓,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.7">乃行.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.8">君王喜之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-2a.9">焉命陳公狂止之.【14】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.3 (STRIPS 9-10) MACHENGYUAN 9: 177 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a.1">陳公狂既聽命,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a.2">乃逝整師徒.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a.3">陳公乃就軍執事人,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a.4">君魯 [...] 【9】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a.5">[...] 又復於君王以逞師徒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a.6">師徒皆懼,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-3a.7">乃各得其行.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.4 (STRIPS 10, 7-8) MACHENGYUAN 9: 177, 175-176 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.1">復聽命於君王:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.2">"君王不知臣之無才,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.3">命臣相執【10】事人</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.4">整師徒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.5">不知進師啟極於王所</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.6">而止師徒乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.7">不知其啓卒陵行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.8">遂內王卒</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-4a.9">而毋止師【7】徒乎?</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.5 (STRIP 8) MACHENGYUAN 9: 176 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-5a.1">王謂陳公:</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-5a.2">“如內王卒</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-5a.3">而毋止師徒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-5a.4">毋亦善乎?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-5a.5">陳[公] [...] 【8】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.6 (STRIPS 6, 11) MACHENGYUAN 9: 174, 178 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.1">[...]  此,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.2">君王不知狂之無才,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.3">命狂相執【6】事人</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.4">整師徒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.5">執事人必善命之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.6">命相輔轅[=挾車],</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.7">五人於伍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.8">十人於行.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.9">行列不成,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.10">隊率隊,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-6a.11">命從廢.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.7 (STRIPS 11, 13, 12) MACHENGYUAN 9: 178, 181, 180 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.1">小人將【11】車爲主焉.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.2">又持八鼓五爯,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.3">鉦鐃以左,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.4">錞于以右,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.5">金鐸以坐,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.6">木鐸以起,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.7">鼓以進之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.8">鼙以止之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.9">X烈【13】以臧士,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.10">喬山以退之.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.11">有所謂威,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.12">有所謂恭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.13">有所謂卻,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.14">有所謂一,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-7a.15">有所謂專.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.8 (STRIPS 12, 3) MACHENGYUAN 9: 180, 171 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a.1">陳公狂焉坐,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a.2">楚邦之故【12】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a.3">戰於蔡湫, 咎,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a.4">師不絕.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a.5">酓[=熊]雪, 子皮）與巴人戰於鴼州，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a.6">師不絕,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-8a.7">焉得其猨旗.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.9 (STRIPS 3, 2, 4) MACHENGYUAN 9: 171, 170, 173 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-9a.1">屈甹與巴命尹戰於息(?)，【3】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-9a.2">戰而持之(?).</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-9a.3">先君武王與鄖(?)人戰於蒲寞 (?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-9a.4">師不絕.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-9a.5">先君文[王] [...] 【2】[...] 戰於涂漳之滸,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-9a.6">師不絕.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.10 (STRIPS 4-5, 15) MACHENGYUAN 9: 173-174, 183 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.1">又與晉人戰於兩棠,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.2">師不絕.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.3">如既至於仇人之間，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.4">將出師,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.5">既斯移軍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.6">左右【4】司馬進於將軍,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.7">命出師徒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-10a.8">將軍乃許諾左右司馬 [...] 【5】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.11 (STRIPS 15-16) MACHENGYUAN 9: 183-184 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.1">[...]  之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.2">師徒乃出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.3">背軍而陣,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.4">將軍後出,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.5">焉名【15】之弇行,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.6">如閟,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.7">如逆閟,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.8">如關術(?),</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.9">如攻隊,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.10">如御追,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-11a.11">必慎 [...]【16】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.12 (STRIP 17) MACHENGYUAN 9: 185 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-12a.1">[...] 檐徒,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-12a.2">周其徒衛.</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.13 (STRIPS 17, 19) MACHENGYUAN 9: 185, 187 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.1">如既堞城焉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.2">陳兩和而紉之,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.3">必慎.【簡17】</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.4">陣於阜岡 (?) [=陵崗]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.5">則鴈飛.</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.6">陣於埸野,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.7">深艸, 霜露,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-13a.8">車則【簡19】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.14 (STRIP 18) MACHENGYUAN 9: 186 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-14a" ed="tls" n="001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-14a.1">徒甲居後,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-14a.2">陳於障,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-14a.3">則徒甲進退【18】</seg></p>

<p source="SHANGBO.CHENGGONGZHIBING 9.56.15 (STRIP 20) MACHENGYUAN 9: 187 TR. MARCO CABOARA"><pb xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-15a" ed="tls" n="001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-15a.1">[...] 兩陣後，[...]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-15a.2">乃右麻左麻，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-15a.3">陣後若繩，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-15a.4">或兩陣前，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0084_tls_001-15a.5">右麻左 [...]【20】</seg></p>

